    </figcaption>

        </figure>
        
    
    <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

                    <span class="opener__topics ">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/technology">Technology</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        The Rise and Fall of Terrorgram: Inside a Global Online Hate Network
    </h1>

        <h2 class="opener__dek " style="display: none" >            How a cadre of white supremacists used the loosely moderated social media platform Telegram to inspire lethal violence — until authorities took them down.
        </h2>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--center     " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
