    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/zero-trust">Zero Trust</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/biden-executive-order-cybersecurity-microsoft-solarwinds-hack">
                                    Following a Series of Government Hacks, Biden Closes Out His Administration With New Cybersecurity Order
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The executive order follows a ProPublica investigation that found Microsoft prioritized profit over security, leaving the federal government vulnerable to the largest hack in U.S. history. Vendors must now demonstrate that their products are secure.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/renee-dudley">Renee Dudley</a>,
